review: I have been consulting wahida from 2 years from my first pregnancy to now for my second pregnancy as well though I m out of Chennai now.. she is such a wonderful doctor , very friendly and patient*  ***** *********** *********** *********** She erased all my fear and doubts.. I definitely recommend wahida for all my friends and relatives

I have consulted the doctor twice and both the sessions were satisfactory. *** ********* *** **** **** ****. I have extreme satisfaction with the results. Supposedly, one should have to wait around 30 minutes for the consultation. Everything is fine with service and hospitality.

review: Dr Wahida Suresh is an amazing human and then a doctor. When I visited her for the first time I really felt the vibe and that made me fixed to continue with her during my whole pregnancy. I recommend her for any women who wants a reliable and a positive attitude doctor for pregnancy journey.

I have visited this doctor on Dec17,2018.  I have been asked to pay 300 rupees and after paying I am on my way to hostel. I got call from Apollo to pay consultation amount and I was suprised to know the fee as 1000 rupees. I was in hurry to reach hostel within time, so without hesitation I came back and paid the entire amount. I am surprised to see the consultation amount is only 500 in practo.  please refund me the extra amt.
Last  two years back i visited doctor for pregnancy,excellent care  and treatment  given ,now am happy with child
Wonderful doctor and human being as well. Very friendly with the patients and provides excellent care.

It was my first consultation with Dr. Wahida Suresh. She performed the diagnosis and treatment in an excellent way. I am perfectly fine now. There was around 45 minutes of waiting period even after a fixed appointment. It was mostly because of the crowd.
